Speedbreaker and Drag Strip step out of the Dark Avian, Speedbreaker is
holding a odd shaped metalic box. Astroblast then rockets out of the
horizen, transfroming into train mode, slowing his progress. Wildrider and
Dead-End step out of him as he transforms. "Okay, SPeedbreaker give me the
personality components, Wildrider, Dead-End, give me the cassetes". With
that Astroblast recieves them all. He slowly inserts a small pink cylander
into each cassete. After a while of waiting, Wildrider speaks up, "What the
slag is taking so long, I wanna bust something up," but is stoped form a
blast from behind. Motormaster emerges, put back together, his gun smoking.
"Whats going on, I have a splitting headache" he spits. Wildrider rights
himself, his shoulder smoking from the wound, " uh sir, we were just,
what's that" he shouts pointing towards the flying jet (Triggerhappy)
rocketing towards them. "HHHMMMMM, could it be those slagging Maximal cats
trying to finish me off" Motormaster states. All the Stunticons raise their
weapons towards the jet. "Announce yourself" Astroblast says over the
commlink, hoping the jet will hear him.
